# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __itruediv__, __ifloordiv__, __imod__ across all 5 pathlib subjects
#
# 5 classes x 3 methods = 15 rows.
# All values are false; pathlib defines no in-place division/modulo operators.
# pathlib defines __truediv__ (wave 659) for path joining but NOT __itruediv__:
# the /= operator on paths falls back to __truediv__ and rebinds the variable.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

